data.description: Drive above the city to be impressed by this custom built residence featuring  4,044 usable square feet, never ending unobstructed views of the Angeles National Forest, Mt Lukens and Angeles National golf course. Mountain skylines that connect the sky and earth for eye opening views of mother nature's beauty can be seen from inside this home or by walking out to any of the four secure balconies while enjoying your favorite beverage. Enjoy the fireplace, hardwood floors, tall ceilings, and mountain views in the living room that may result to be your favorite room in the house to feel cozy. The  Hardwood floors will lead you to a bright private room being used as an office, a music room or a 5th bedroom, that closes for privacy by sliding decorative barn doors together. Hardwood floors and mountain views can also be seen from the family room and the 4 spacious bedrooms that are featured. This home has 4 full baths, the master bath has dual sinks, a jet tub, a Shower  and updated travertine tile finishes. The very large Master bedroom features an outdoor balcony, a gigantic walk in closet, also a 2nd walk in closet.  this home features an indoor gym  to get you into great shape.  The Kitchen ceiling brings in added style, pendent lights brighten the glass backsplash, quartz countertops and breakfast bar. A five burner stove, an oven, dishwasher and dual refrigerator are surrounded by the updated white wood cabinets for plenty of storage. This home is designed with tall ceilings, crown moldings, travertine tile, hardwood floors and an open floorplan that connects the dining room, kitchen, family room, makes this home feel very spacious. Enjoy an outdoor meal in the backyard, wooden patio. There are no neighbors behind this home because it is elevated sitting high to enjoy endless views.  One bedroom is on the main floor, the master bedroom & 2 more bedrooms are downstairs. The 2 garage with home access. the home is securely gated with rod iron fencing throughout.  Palm trees and low irrigation landscaping will conserve water. There is a complete house water filtered system that is included. The home has 2 A/C units and 2 heater units for upstairs and downstairs independently operated to reduce expense. The road to this property is not traveled, very few cars. Fast access to Freeways. This sellers have taken great measures to keep the home in excellent condition. This home comes with a complete home warranty included,  call the listing agent for details.
